Interface ICounterNode

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICounter<T>, ICounterSet
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ICounterNode
    Shared abstraction layer for both ICounterSet and ICounter.

    $Id$
    Author:
